\u0633\u064f\u0641\u0652\u064a\u064e\u0627\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u062b\u0651\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0651 \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u062b\u064e\u0644\u0627\u062b\u064e\u0629\u064c \u0645\u0650\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0635\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0652\u0631\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17455,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/01\/02\/qadr-reward-sabr-shukr\/","url_meta":{"origin":26031,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Shukr: Believer is rewarded for patience or gratitude","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 2, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019d ibn Abi Waqqas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cI am amazed by the believer. If he is granted goodness, he praises Allah and is grateful. If he is afflicted with a calamity, he praises Allah and is patient. The believer is rewarded\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37746,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/03\/14\/shukr-sabr-sawm\/","url_meta":{"origin":26031,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Gratitude: Thankfulness to Allah rewarded like patience","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 14, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Sinan ibn Sannah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe one who eats gratefully has a reward similar to one who fasts patiently.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 1765 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0633\u0650\u0646\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0633\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0629\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0623\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0644\u064e\u0645\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":21803,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/01\/31\/umar-best-days-sabr\/","url_meta":{"origin":26031,"position":3},"title":"Umar on Sabr: Our best days were because of our patience","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 31, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdulla ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: Umar ibn Al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cVerily, the best days we knew were due to patience. If patience were to take the form of a man, it would be a nobleman.\u201d Source: al-S\u0323abr wal-Thawa\u0304b\u00a06 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0639\u064f\u0648\u062f\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24287,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/01\/22\/ali-sabr-iman-head-body\/","url_meta":{"origin":26031,"position":4},"title":"Ali on Sabr: Patience to faith like a head to a body","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 22, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Masruq reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cVerily, patience is to faith as the head is to the body. If the head is cut, the body will perish.\u201d Then, Ali raised his voice and he said, \u201cNo doubt, there is no faith for one\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40067,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/05\/13\/sabr-rizq\/","url_meta":{"origin":26031,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Sabr: Patience is best provision from Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 13, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cA servant is not provided with anything better and vaster than patience.\u201d Source: al-Mustadrak \u2018ala\u0301 al-S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323ayn 3552 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0631\u064f\u0632\u0650\u0642\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0